Just so you guys know, I finished working on revising scenario #118. 
Passage ways became wider and where teleporters go makes better sense
(at least in my head).  Oh yea, hopefully the faeries will be smart
enough to take advantage of the teleporters I placed in the water so
that theoritically the same faerie could visit all the water areas.

If there are any more scenarios of mine that *you* think need
revising, let me know.
